leadingComments.value:
* * Creates an instance of WebsocketDatasource. This datasource will try to connect to the speficied websocket endpoint. * 
     *    var source = {
     *      endpoint: 'ws://192.168.3.32:3000/pathToWebsocketEndpoint';
     *    };
     * 
     *    linechart = new proteic.Linechart(new proteic.WebsocketDatasource(source));
     *
* * If new data is available, this datasource will forward the data records to the chart, which automatically repaint the chart with these new records. * @param {any} source A websocket endpoint. If invalid, this class will throw an Error. * * @memberOf WebsocketDatasource
